<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kāntaḷūrccālai kalamaṟutta kovirā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>kecaripa<hi rend="grantha">nma</hi> rkku yāṇṭu pattā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>vatu <hi rend="grantha">brahma</hi> teyam ciṟupaḻuvūr tiruvā<supplied reason="omitted">la</supplied>ntuṟaiuṭaiya ma<hi rend="grantha">hā</hi>tevarkku Aṭikaḷ <unclear>pa</unclear>ḻuveṭṭa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>raiyā kaṇṭan maṟavanār peruntiṟat taraiyan cuntiracoḻanen nicata<supplied reason="omitted">m</supplied> Irunāḻi tumpaip paḷḷi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ttāmam paṟiccaṭṭa vaicca nila<unclear>m</unclear> Ivvūr kiḻakkuvār nān kuṭutta nilattukku kiḻpāṟ kellai māṟa 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>n Iravi nilattukku<note n="281-1">Read meṟkum.</note>meRkkam<note n="281-2">Read teṉpāṟ.</note>tenpuṟk kellai Aḷakkanār kuḻikku vaṭakkum mipār kellai ko
<lb n="6" break="no"/>vaṇivaṭi vi<unclear>n</unclear>taip peṟṟa peṟṟukkuk kiḻakku nokkipona varampukku teṟkkum
<lb n="7"/>Ivvicaitta perunān kellaiyuḷ ḷakappaṭṭa nilam Uṇṇilam Aḻivinṟi viṟ
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṟu vilaiyāvaṇam ceytu kuṭutten Araiyan cuntaracoḻanen Itu pa<hi rend="grantha">nmā</hi>ye<hi rend="grantha">śvara rakṣai</hi> <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
